# Project CSS Guidelines

## UI Component Library
- **Use shadcn-svelte** for UI components instead of daisyUI
- Prefer shadcn-svelte components for consistent design system
- If shadcn-svelte doesn't have a needed component, use custom Tailwind CSS classes

## CSS Framework Rules
- **DO NOT** use daisyUI classes or CSS
- Use Tailwind CSS utility classes for styling
- Write custom CSS only when necessary

## Svelte 5 Rules
- Use Svelte 5 syntax and features

# Latest Svelte Kit Rules
- Use latest svelte kit 

## Svelte 5 Effect Rules
- **DO NOT** use async functions directly inside `$effect()` blocks
- Reference: https://github.com/sveltejs/svelte/issues/9520
- Use separate async functions and call them from within effects if needed

